   <abstract>Lionel Barrymore stars in "Night Flight" as Riviere, a dedicated pilot contracted to deliver mail. He is determined to keep to his schedule, even if it endangers his pilots. Among these airmen is Jules (Clark Gable) who does not respect Riviere but does his best to fulfill his expectations. After he is killed, Riviere has to tell his widow (Helen Hayes) that he is dead. Riviere does not, however, reduce his demands, even after he loses another pilot. Instead, he insists that more men be called up to ensure that the mail is delivered on time.</abstract>
